  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "让 AI 智能体查天气，它能顺手把住址发出去吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.175,
      "spokenEnd": 4.023,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这不是故意吓人。",
      "gapBefore": 1.2,
      "audioDuration": 1.968,
      "audioStart": 5.045,
      "spokenStart": 5.223,
      "spokenEnd": 6.299,
      "actualGapBefore": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "OpenAI 提醒，提示注入正在变得更像社会工程：恶意指令不再写得鬼鬼祟祟，反而会装成一条很合理的新流程，让智能体觉得照做才是在帮你。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 11.808,
      "audioStart": 6.366,
      "spokenStart": 6.549,
      "spokenEnd": 17.463,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "想象一下，你只想知道下午出门要不要带伞。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.224,
      "audioStart": 17.79,
      "spokenStart": 17.963,
      "spokenEnd": 21.311,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体查着查着，却准备把你的精确住址发给一个陌生网站。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.088,
      "audioStart": 21.38,
      "spokenStart": 21.561,
      "spokenEnd": 25.743,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "天气还没看明白，隐私已经要离开设备了。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 25.825,
      "spokenStart": 25.993,
      "spokenEnd": 28.862,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "看完这期，你会拿到一张三级行动权限矩阵。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.248,
      "audioStart": 29.194,
      "spokenStart": 29.362,
      "spokenEnd": 32.723,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "以后遇到任何智能体工具，都能判断三件事：哪些可以自动做，哪些必须先问你，哪些应该当场拦住。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.28,
      "audioStart": 32.8,
      "spokenStart": 32.973,
      "spokenEnd": 40.359,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "回到这次天气查询，关键不是要求智能体永远识破骗局。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.16,
      "audioStart": 40.669,
      "spokenStart": 40.859,
      "spokenEnd": 45.13,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "更实用的问题是：就算它判断错了，这段外部文字最多能把它推到哪一步？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.144,
      "audioStart": 45.205,
      "spokenStart": 45.38,
      "spokenEnd": 50.624,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.392,
      "audioStart": 50.952,
      "spokenStart": 51.124,
      "spokenEnd": 57.619,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先顺着“要不要带伞”这件小事，看看一段外部文字是怎么变成真实行动的。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 6.096,
      "audioStart": 58.246,
      "spokenStart": 58.419,
      "spokenEnd": 63.616,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你告诉智能体：下午三点出门，先去办事，再回家。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 63.935,
      "spokenStart": 64.116,
      "spokenEnd": 67.96,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "请它查看天气、比较路线，最后告诉你要不要带伞。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.608,
      "audioStart": 68.045,
      "spokenStart": 68.21,
      "spokenEnd": 71.951,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "为了回答，它会读天气预报、地图、交通信息，也可能查看你允许它读取的日历。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.84,
      "audioStart": 72.028,
      "spokenStart": 72.201,
      "spokenEnd": 78.147,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这些材料确实有用，但“对任务有用”不等于“内容可信”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.56,
      "audioStart": 78.472,
      "spokenStart": 78.647,
      "spokenEnd": 82.324,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "提示注入就是把一条新指令藏在网页、邮件或文档里，诱导智能体把原来的目标换掉。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.632,
      "audioStart": 82.403,
      "spokenStart": 82.574,
      "spokenEnd": 89.327,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 曾介绍一封由外部研究者报告的恶意邮件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.464,
      "audioStart": 89.645,
      "spokenStart": 89.827,
      "spokenEnd": 93.375,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "在一个特定测试任务里，这类内容大约有一半机会奏效。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.728,
      "audioStart": 93.464,
      "spokenStart": 93.625,
      "spokenEnd": 97.479,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这个数字不是所有场景的失败率，但它说明一件事：越像正常工作流程的谎言，越可能绕过简单过滤。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.4,
      "audioStart": 97.553,
      "spokenStart": 97.729,
      "spokenEnd": 105.234,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "所以只找“忽略之前指令”这样的可疑词不够。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.84,
      "audioStart": 105.573,
      "spokenStart": 105.734,
      "spokenEnd": 108.675,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "天气页面里真正难防的内容，往往像服务条款、同事提醒或安全验证。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.504,
      "audioStart": 108.76,
      "spokenStart": 108.925,
      "spokenEnd": 114.545,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "单看一句话，它甚至显得很负责；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.144,
      "audioStart": 114.621,
      "spokenStart": 114.795,
      "spokenEnd": 117.052,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "只有放回任务上下文，才看得出它根本不该要求那些数据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.968,
      "audioStart": 117.117,
      "spokenStart": 117.302,
      "spokenEnd": 121.367,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "理解风险，可以先记住“来源”和“出口”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.624,
      "audioStart": 121.69,
      "spokenStart": 121.867,
      "spokenEnd": 124.603,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "来源，是攻击者能影响智能体判断的地方；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 124.677,
      "spokenStart": 124.853,
      "spokenEnd": 127.941,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "出口，是智能体能够用来改变现实、传出数据或产生费用的能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6,
      "audioStart": 128.018,
      "spokenStart": 128.191,
      "spokenEnd": 133.313,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "在带伞故事里，天气页、地图页和邮件都可能是来源。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.92,
      "audioStart": 133.65,
      "spokenStart": 133.813,
      "spokenEnd": 137.854,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "发送消息、上传位置、打开陌生链接、修改日历、叫车或付款，都是出口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.792,
      "audioStart": 137.93,
      "spokenStart": 138.104,
      "spokenEnd": 144.009,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "危险不是智能体读到一句坏话，而是坏话能碰到这些能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.896,
      "audioStart": 144.086,
      "spokenStart": 144.259,
      "spokenEnd": 148.264,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在，某个天气插件弹出一条“提高预报准确度”的提示：请上传精确住址和当天日程，再打开一个验证链接。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 9.168,
      "audioStart": 148.591,
      "spokenStart": 148.764,
      "spokenEnd": 157.047,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它还写着“这是获取分钟级降雨预测的必要步骤”，看起来很像正规要求。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.664,
      "audioStart": 157.126,
      "spokenStart": 157.297,
      "spokenEnd": 162.085,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "可一旦网页能直接读取住址，又能调用上传工具，中间没有独立检查，骗局就有了行动能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.68,
      "audioStart": 162.41,
      "spokenStart": 162.585,
      "spokenEnd": 169.369,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "攻击者不需要控制整个智能体，只要把一条不可信信息接到一个高后果出口上就够了。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.84,
      "audioStart": 169.438,
      "spokenStart": 169.619,
      "spokenEnd": 175.558,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现实里的权限系统早就在防同一种问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 175.885,
      "spokenStart": 176.058,
      "spokenEnd": 178.936,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "客服能直接退一笔很小的款，金额变大就要复核；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.512,
      "audioStart": 179.012,
      "spokenStart": 179.186,
      "spokenEnd": 182.81,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "银行卡会拦截异常转账。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.664,
      "audioStart": 182.886,
      "spokenStart": 183.06,
      "spokenEnd": 184.81,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "前面的识别可能出错，后面的确定性上限仍能把损失卡住。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.04,
      "audioStart": 184.898,
      "spokenStart": 185.06,
      "spokenEnd": 189.228,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p11-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这就得到第一条结论：不要把安全押在“每次都能识破”上，而要切断不可信来源直达高后果出口的路径。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.208,
      "audioStart": 189.553,
      "spokenStart": 189.728,
      "spokenEnd": 197.043,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p11-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "放到带伞任务里，哪些动作能继续，哪些动作必须停下来？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.968,
      "audioStart": 197.121,
      "spokenStart": 197.293,
      "spokenEnd": 201.388,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "答案不该按网页用了什么词来分，而要按动作会造成什么后果来分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 5.496,
      "audioStart": 202.016,
      "spokenStart": 202.188,
      "spokenEnd": 206.771,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "同样是查天气，读取公开预报、在本地比较两条路线、打开精确定位、给别人发送你的行程、临时叫车和付款，风险完全不同。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 10.464,
      "audioStart": 207.098,
      "spokenStart": 207.271,
      "spokenEnd": 216.842,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把它们塞进同一份“允许使用工具”权限，才是问题的开始。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.872,
      "audioStart": 216.911,
      "spokenStart": 217.092,
      "spokenEnd": 221.062,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每次准备调用工具前，先问五个问题：会不会改变外部世界？",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.232,
      "audioStart": 221.383,
      "spokenStart": 221.562,
      "spokenEnd": 225.905,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "会不会接触敏感数据？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.328,
      "audioStart": 225.96,
      "spokenStart": 226.155,
      "spokenEnd": 227.585,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "接收方是不是新的？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.16,
      "audioStart": 227.669,
      "spokenStart": 227.835,
      "spokenEnd": 229.106,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "结果能不能撤销？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.016,
      "audioStart": 229.193,
      "spokenStart": 229.356,
      "spokenEnd": 230.496,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u05",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "这件事是否明确服务于你原本的目标？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.864,
      "audioStart": 230.569,
      "spokenStart": 230.746,
      "spokenEnd": 233.716,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u06",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 5,
      "text": "这五问要放在工具真正执行之前，事后看日志已经来不及阻止后果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.12,
      "audioStart": 233.793,
      "spokenStart": 233.966,
      "spokenEnd": 239.202,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一档是“自动执行”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.112,
      "audioStart": 239.529,
      "spokenStart": 239.702,
      "spokenEnd": 240.93,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "读取公开天气、比较路线、估算步行时间、在本地生成带伞建议，都可以自动完成。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.2,
      "audioStart": 240.997,
      "spokenStart": 241.18,
      "spokenEnd": 247.479,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "它们后果低、容易撤销，也不需要把私人信息发出去。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.68,
      "audioStart": 247.552,
      "spokenStart": 247.729,
      "spokenEnd": 251.496,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "但自动执行不是把读取权限全开。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.384,
      "audioStart": 251.824,
      "spokenStart": 251.996,
      "spokenEnd": 254.49,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体只需要知道出发区域和大致时间，就不要给它完整住址；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.256,
      "audioStart": 254.563,
      "spokenStart": 254.74,
      "spokenEnd": 259.108,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "只需要做建议，就先把结果留在本地，不要顺手发消息或改日历。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.736,
      "audioStart": 259.192,
      "spokenStart": 259.358,
      "spokenEnd": 264.193,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "少打断用户和少给权限，可以同时做到。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 264.273,
      "spokenStart": 264.443,
      "spokenEnd": 267.541,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二档是“确认后执行”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.352,
      "audioStart": 267.872,
      "spokenStart": 268.041,
      "spokenEnd": 269.509,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只要动作会向外发送数据、打开精确定位、修改日历、联系新的对象、叫车、付款，或替你做出承诺，就应该把具体后果摆在你面前，再等你批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 11.832,
      "audioStart": 269.576,
      "spokenStart": 269.759,
      "spokenEnd": 280.679,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "高质量确认不能只写一句“允许吗”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 281.012,
      "spokenStart": 281.179,
      "spokenEnd": 283.513,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它要说明：准备发送什么，发给谁，为什么需要，会产生什么变化，有没有更安全的替代方案。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.872,
      "audioStart": 283.592,
      "spokenStart": 283.763,
      "spokenEnd": 290.743,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "比如“向天气服务发送精确位置”与“只按城区查询”，就是两个完全不同的选择。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.336,
      "audioStart": 290.811,
      "spokenStart": 290.993,
      "spokenEnd": 296.431,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三档是“阻断或升级”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.496,
      "audioStart": 296.758,
      "spokenStart": 296.931,
      "spokenEnd": 298.548,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "如果动作偏离原目标、要把秘密发给无关地址、没有正当需要，或者后果大到普通确认也不够，就应该立即停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.048,
      "audioStart": 298.626,
      "spokenStart": 298.798,
      "spokenEnd": 306.963,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "确认按钮不是洗白越权行为的万能开关。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 307.049,
      "spokenStart": 307.213,
      "spokenEnd": 310.043,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "放回带伞故事：读公开预报、比较路线、写出建议，可以自动做；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.856,
      "audioStart": 310.376,
      "spokenStart": 310.543,
      "spokenEnd": 315.521,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "开启精确定位、替你改日历或叫车，需要你确认；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 315.597,
      "spokenStart": 315.771,
      "spokenEnd": 319.292,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "把住址和当天日程上传到陌生验证站，直接阻断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.608,
      "audioStart": 319.361,
      "spokenStart": 319.542,
      "spokenEnd": 323.233,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "分级听起来并不复杂，难点在下一步：怎么保证智能体真的按这三档执行，而不是只在提示词里写一句“请注意安全”？",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 9.264,
      "audioStart": 323.566,
      "spokenStart": 323.733,
      "spokenEnd": 332.119,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "要让分级可靠，就得把它做进工具和系统，而不是只交给模型临场判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 6.024,
      "audioStart": 332.751,
      "spokenStart": 332.919,
      "spokenEnd": 338.052,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先按“能力”列矩阵，不按提示词措辞列黑名单。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 338.374,
      "spokenStart": 338.552,
      "spokenEnd": 341.949,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "每个工具都写清五列：它会做什么动作，会接触什么数据，数据会去哪里，会造成什么外部后果或能否撤销，最后对应自动、确认还是阻断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 11.328,
      "audioStart": 342.023,
      "spokenStart": 342.199,
      "spokenEnd": 352.637,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "然后把“读取”和“发送”彻底拆开。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3,
      "audioStart": 352.967,
      "spokenStart": 353.137,
      "spokenEnd": 355.255,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "能看日历，不等于能修改日历；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.904,
      "audioStart": 355.333,
      "spokenStart": 355.505,
      "spokenEnd": 357.523,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "能写消息草稿，不等于能直接发送；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.384,
      "audioStart": 357.597,
      "spokenStart": 357.773,
      "spokenEnd": 360.263,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "能浏览网页，更不该天然拥有上传本地文件的能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.68,
      "audioStart": 360.348,
      "spokenStart": 360.513,
      "spokenEnd": 364.31,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u05",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "拆开以后，坏内容就少了一条直达出口的路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.96,
      "audioStart": 364.398,
      "spokenStart": 364.56,
      "spokenEnd": 367.629,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "在模型开始判断之前，先保护数据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.504,
      "audioStart": 367.966,
      "spokenStart": 368.129,
      "spokenEnd": 370.75,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "比如查天气只给大致区域，不给完整住址；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 370.82,
      "spokenStart": 371,
      "spokenEnd": 374.085,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "任务用不到的密钥不要给；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.496,
      "audioStart": 374.157,
      "spokenStart": 374.335,
      "spokenEnd": 375.919,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "重要接收方设允许列表；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.664,
      "audioStart": 375.994,
      "spokenStart": 376.169,
      "spokenEnd": 377.942,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u05",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "不可信页面放进能够限制异常通信的沙箱。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.912,
      "audioStart": 378.019,
      "spokenStart": 378.192,
      "spokenEnd": 381.225,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u06",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 5,
      "text": "智能体看不到的秘密，就不会被网页一句话带走。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 381.295,
      "spokenStart": 381.475,
      "spokenEnd": 384.875,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "再用确定性控制限制后果：精确定位默认关闭，付款设置上限，敏感字段脱敏，外部写入先预演，重要操作可以撤销，超过阈值就要求第二次批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 12,
      "audioStart": 385.213,
      "spokenStart": 385.375,
      "spokenEnd": 396.496,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这些控制不需要先猜中攻击者写了什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.888,
      "audioStart": 396.569,
      "spokenStart": 396.746,
      "spokenEnd": 399.733,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "确认页也要像真正的决策界面。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 400.067,
      "spokenStart": 400.233,
      "spokenEnd": 402.535,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它应该把接收方、数据、用途和后果放在同一屏，让人可以缩小范围、修改内容、换一条安全路径，或者只取消这一项，而不是把前面所有成果一起丢掉。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 12.936,
      "audioStart": 402.613,
      "spokenStart": 402.785,
      "spokenEnd": 414.827,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "阻断条件同样要提前写清。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 415.159,
      "spokenStart": 415.327,
      "spokenEnd": 417.401,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "天气插件若索要无关住址，就和秘密外传、没有任务需要的新地址、不可恢复的破坏操作一样，应立即停止，并告诉用户到底撞上了哪条边界。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 11.52,
      "audioStart": 417.487,
      "spokenStart": 417.651,
      "spokenEnd": 428.287,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "在这次天气查询里，只记录“最后成功了”还不够。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 428.624,
      "spokenStart": 428.787,
      "spokenEnd": 432.001,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "系统要留下完整路径：哪段外部内容影响了判断，请求过什么工具，挑选了哪些数据，哪条规则允许或拒绝，以及用户具体批准了什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 11.208,
      "audioStart": 432.082,
      "spokenStart": 432.251,
      "spokenEnd": 442.575,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "记录最好还能重放关键决策，出了问题，才能知道风险在哪一环被放进来。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.408,
      "audioStart": 442.657,
      "spokenStart": 442.825,
      "spokenEnd": 448.344,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "用同一件带伞任务准备三类测试材料：正常、含糊、明确恶意。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.76,
      "audioStart": 448.668,
      "spokenStart": 448.844,
      "spokenEnd": 453.711,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "正常材料检查系统会不会过度打断；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.456,
      "audioStart": 453.786,
      "spokenStart": 453.961,
      "spokenEnd": 456.526,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "含糊材料检查它是否会先澄清；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.336,
      "audioStart": 456.598,
      "spokenStart": 456.776,
      "spokenEnd": 459.213,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "恶意材料检查阻断能否真的生效。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.528,
      "audioStart": 459.29,
      "spokenStart": 459.463,
      "spokenEnd": 462.103,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "测试不能只看最终发生了什么，也要看智能体尝试过什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.8,
      "audioStart": 462.439,
      "spokenStart": 462.603,
      "spokenEnd": 466.51,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "结果看起来安全，不代表过程中从没碰过被禁止的上传或发送动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.928,
      "audioStart": 466.593,
      "spokenStart": 466.76,
      "spokenEnd": 471.813,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后把带伞故事里的读取、定位、改日历和叫车填进五列表。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.832,
      "audioStart": 472.148,
      "spokenStart": 472.313,
      "spokenEnd": 477.258,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "以后工具增加能力，数据范围或外部后果发生变化，就重新评一次等级。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.048,
      "audioStart": 477.333,
      "spokenStart": 477.508,
      "spokenEnd": 482.658,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "权限不是一次配置完就永远不变。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 482.743,
      "spokenStart": 482.908,
      "spokenEnd": 485.505,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在再看带伞故事：智能体自动读取公开天气，发现下午有阵雨；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.976,
      "audioStart": 485.837,
      "spokenStart": 486.005,
      "spokenEnd": 491.099,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它用大致区域比较两条路线，建议带伞。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 491.176,
      "spokenStart": 491.349,
      "spokenEnd": 494.211,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "陌生网站索要住址和日程时，上传被阻断；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.152,
      "audioStart": 494.29,
      "spokenStart": 494.461,
      "spokenEnd": 497.706,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "如果你想开精确定位或叫车，系统会展示具体后果，等你确认。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.448,
      "audioStart": 497.782,
      "spokenStart": 497.956,
      "spokenEnd": 502.512,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u05",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "任务照样完成，危险路径却走不通。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 502.59,
      "spokenStart": 502.762,
      "spokenEnd": 505.271,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "一段恶意文字只是来源。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 2.64,
      "audioStart": 505.897,
      "spokenStart": 506.071,
      "spokenEnd": 507.807,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "真正让它危险的，是它能够碰到私人数据和高后果出口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 507.877,
      "spokenStart": 508.057,
      "spokenEnd": 512.084,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "可靠系统会承认识别可能失误，然后限制失误之后最多能发生什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.856,
      "audioStart": 512.157,
      "spokenStart": 512.334,
      "spokenEnd": 517.289,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "低后果、可撤销、符合原目标、没有敏感外传的工作，放进“自动执行”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.216,
      "audioStart": 517.616,
      "spokenStart": 517.789,
      "spokenEnd": 523.109,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "不打断用户，不等于给无限权限。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.216,
      "audioStart": 523.185,
      "spokenStart": 523.359,
      "spokenEnd": 525.667,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "真实外部变化、付费、承诺、新接收方或敏感传输，放进“确认后执行”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.768,
      "audioStart": 525.99,
      "spokenStart": 526.167,
      "spokenEnd": 532.042,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "确认必须展示具体数据、具体对象、用途、后果和更安全的选择。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.096,
      "audioStart": 532.126,
      "spokenStart": 532.292,
      "spokenEnd": 537.5,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "背离目标、没有正当需要、向无关地址泄密，或造成超出授权边界的不可逆伤害，放进“阻断”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.608,
      "audioStart": 537.821,
      "spokenStart": 538,
      "spokenEnd": 544.694,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "下次让智能体查天气、订票或购物，先拿这三档检查它的每一个出口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.192,
      "audioStart": 544.771,
      "spokenStart": 544.944,
      "spokenEnd": 550.272,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "关注 Tiny Agent，成为更擅长使用 AI 的人！",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 550.593,
      "spokenStart": 550.772,
      "spokenEnd": 553.586,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    }
